                    <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#7a7a7a' fontsize='13'>Which Dallas–Fort Worth Cities and Counties appreciated the most over the past 10 years?</run>
                    <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
