                    <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000'>• Home values increased an average of </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000'>168%</run>
                    <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000'> across DFW over the past decade. • </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000'>Wilmer</run>
                    <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000'> experienced the highest appreciation. • </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000'>Dallas County</run>
                    <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000'> posted the strongest county-wide growth. </run>
                    <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000'>• </run>
